  * Improve detection of Debian version when there is a "tie" in
    APT's sources.list.  Patch by Giovanni Mascellani.  (Closes: #540208)
  * Fix test for PID file in init-functions.  Patch by Keith O'Brien.
    (Closes: #545896)
