  * Remove duplicate --retry 5 from start-stop-daemon call.  (Closes: #165395)
  * Fix bugs in the init script registry code.  (Closes: #165038)

 -- Chris Lawrence <lawrencc@debian.org>  Tue, 22 Oct 2002 06:23:03 -0500

